text: Compaq was a computer company headquartered in Houston, Texas, provided some of the first IBM PC compatible computers. It was later bought by Hewlett- Packard. It was founded in 1982 and dissolved in 2002. == Other websites == * Official website Category:1980s establishments in Texas Category:1982 establishments in the United States Category:21st-century disestablishments in Texas Category:2002 disestablishments in the United States Category:American computer hardware manufacturers Category:Companies based in Houston
